{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598120/extras/TCK_steam_description_from_screenshots_about.png?t=1731419173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Today's the big day for you and your sister! Mom won't come home until tonight - time to lay down your master plan! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step 1: Raid the house for ritual components.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step 2: Defeat Mom's Wand.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step 3: Bewitch life into your stuffed frog plushie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step 4: ???</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step 5: Infinite benefits...</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598120/extras/TCK_steam_description_from_screenshots_features_2.png?t=1731419173\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pick your twin!</strong> Will you play as Cassie, the chaotic and clumsy sister, or as Layla, the rational mastermind? Each twin comes with her own completely original set of  dialogues and a tailored color-coded hat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a <strong>silly and heartwarming journey</strong> to steal your mom's wand and cast a spell on your frog plushie. What could possibly go wrong?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore a magical house full of minigames</strong>: bounce off the giant staircase, race across a non-euclidian kitchen and open doors to galactic voids</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your best friend is a pig</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful pixel art made with love</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro, SNES-inspired soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller support &amp; accessibility options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Estimated playtime: 1-2 hours</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598120/extras/TCK_steam_description_from_screenshots_accessibility.png?t=1731419173\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller/Gamepad Support, With Rebindable Keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Text Effects Toggle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Non-Pixel Font Toggle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dialogue Speed Option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Camera Shake Toggle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reduced Menu Motion Toggle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easier Minigames Toggle</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Red Runner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/2f062fdb6230e5bb2383a0842428a179d27d2722.jpg"},{"name":"Pasta Frenzy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/522a0484b1aadd6cca4e8af8c3a17a1441285e14.jpg"},{"name":"Speed Demon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/147b5e43b7c5e6819c58a0bd370ec34dc0771170.jpg"},{"name":"The Frog Kids","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/f1ac96b405831fd706ea2b33513f853cb2c100e8.jpg"},{"name":"The Scholar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/6a16a0db064e1f7ce8343a38de1246675f63160b.jpg"},{"name":"Patient Witch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/cf0a8ffbc9894d86a465eb6e9ef0fe7e8dbc4a71.jpg"},{"name":"Map-hacker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/db3d9ccb72d771f4f692e5ddec770aa30c86729f.jpg"},{"name":"Tourist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2598120/